  "texts": [
    "As fast-paced advancements are made in NER, data integration, CV, and LOD, AIKoGAM has the potential to become a tool for researchers and LEAs, fostering a more transparent and secure cultural heritage landscape.",
    "Continued research and collaboration will be key in refining the methodology, and enabling the development of advanced big data models that can analyse, predict, and prevent the illegal trade of cultural heritage.",
    "Giovanelli and Traviglia Journal of Computer Applications in Archaeology DOI: 10.5334/jcaa.130"
  ]
}